00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:30,640
I to više ne izgleda kao ukradeno novac.

393
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,600
Mislim da je to super.

394
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:32,000
Da.

395
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:33,200
To je super za mene.

396
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:33,840
